title: Rep. Levin: Doubling Down on Fossil Fuels Will Increase Transportation Cost Volatility
description: Representative Mike Levin argues that focusing on fossil fuels will worsen transportation cost volatility, citing rising energy costs despite some fuel price decreases. He highlights concerns about the impact of costs on households and the distribution of economic growth.
